20on%20my%20birthday%3B%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20where%20we%20were%20going.%20We%20flew%20to%20San%20Diego%2C%20and%20Joey%20Hamilton%20of%20TLC's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fink-master-what-its-like-getting-tattooed-on-tv-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInk%20Masters%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20did%20the%20tattoo.%20Joey's%20quite%20famous.%20He's%20also%20a%20veteran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222046%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Patriotic%20Kenny%20posing%20for%20a%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a6f256d3e2f1aef369df4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221510%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKenny%20Jary%20got%20his%20first%20tattoo%20thanks%20to%20his%20two%20new%20friends.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kenny%20Jary%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20hurt%20at%20all.%20If%20anything%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20little%20kid%20scratching.%20It's%20just%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-tattoo-fine-line-tattoos-trend-luxury-status-symbol-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmall%20tattoo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20represent%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%20There's%20an%20anchor%2C%20and%20then%20it%20has%20three%20stars%20to%20represent%20Minnesota.%20There%20are%20three%20rings%20to%20represent%20my%20three%20kids%2C%20and%20our%20group%20of%20three%3A%20me%2C%20Amanda%2C%20and%20Jenny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b03aa5ab-fca5-4cd1-adfd-e11acd88a3cc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20believe%20it's%20never%20too%20late%20to%20cross%20something%20off%20your%20bucket%20list%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20people%20should%20cross%20things%20off%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountries-everyone-should-add-to-bucket-list-from-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebucket%20lists%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20life%20goes%20fast.%20One%20minute%20you're%20a%20teenager%20and%20the%20next%20you're%20nearly%2090.%20If%20you%20keep%20waiting%2C%20you%20might%20miss%20your%20chance.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20try%20something%20I've%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20I%20feel%20proud%20and%20alive.%20Recently%2C%20I%20have%20traveled%20to%20new%20places%2C%20flown%20on%20big%20planes%2C%20met%20new%20people%20from%20all%20over%2C%20and%20now%20I%20have%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftattoo-artist-what-not-to-do-when-getting-first-tattoo-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20tattoo%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Each%20time%20I%20try%20something%20new%2C%20it%20reminds%20me%20that%20I%20am%20still%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20been%20the%20Kenny%20I%20am%2C%20way%20up%20until%20right%20now.%20Nothing%20has%20changed%20since%20I%20was%20knee-high%20to%20a%20grasshopper.%20I've%20always%20been%20jolly%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20you%20need%20to%20smile%20and%20be%20jolly%2C%20it%20makes%20the%20world%20go%20round%20and%20makes%20you%20feel%20better.%20Laughter%20is%20most%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221154%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joey%20Hamilton%20with%20client%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a6f2d7fd4fbd083f2967f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22866%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKenny%20Jary%20got%20tattooed%20by%20Joey%20Hamilton%20from%20TLC's%20%26quot%3BInk%20Masters.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kenny%20Jary%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20was%20not%20always%20this%20open%20to%20new%20things.%20When%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20I%20liked%20what%20felt%20safe.%20As%20I%20got%20older%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20trying%20new%20things%20makes%20life%20bigger.%20I%20have%20tried%20traveling%20far%20from%20home%2C%20speaking%20in%20front%20of%20crowds%2C%20and%20sharing%20my%20story%20online.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20felt%20nervous.%20Then%20I%20feel%20excited.%20After%20I%20do%20it%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20leaving%20a%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254223246-f736-4433-a04d-e1c448aba67b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20friendship%20has%20changed%20my%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20trust%20Amanda%20and%20Jenny%20because%20they%20truly%20care%20about%20me.%20They%20listen%20to%20me.%20They%20protect%20me.%20They%20push%20me%20in%20a%20good%20way%2C%20not%20a%20scary%20way.%20They%20want%20me%20to%20have%20a%20full%20life.%20That%20trust%20comes%20from%20time%2C%20honesty%2C%20and%20love.%20Our%20relationship%20is%20important%20because%20we%20support%20each%20other%20and%20are%20family.%20No%20matter%20what%20we're%20doing%2C%20we're%20always%20having%20a%20good%20time%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tell%20everybody%20that%20they're%20my%20daughters%20now%2C%20and%20I%20treat%20them%20just%20like%20my%20own%20daughter.%20Amanda%20and%20Jenny%20have%20brought%20me%20a%20whole%20new%20life%2C%20I%20mean%20that%20sincerely.%20I%20do%20more%20things%20at%2084%20years%20old%20than%20I%20thought%20possible.%20I%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%20and%20do%20things.%20Don't%20get%20me%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fwhat-are-the-symptoms-of-copd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estill%20have%20COPD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20still%20struggle%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20get%20out%20and%20do%20things.%20Four%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20we%20started%20the%20TikTok%20account%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20anything.%20My%20scooter%20broke%20down.%20It%20was%20junk.%20I%20had%20bought%20it%20at%20a%20garage%20sale.%20Then%20I%20had%20the%20good%20fortune%20to%20meet%20these%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20began%20a%20foundation%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20called%20the%20Patriotic%20Kenny%20Foundation.%20I%20got%20my%20scooter%20from%20online%20donations.%20We%20had%20all%20these%20fans%2C%20millions%20of%20them.%20I%20told%20Amanda%20I%20was%20going%20to%20pay%20it%20forward%20with%20scooters.%