0buys%20Chinese%20supersonic%20missiles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773400260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F26%2F03%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-cm-400akg-missile-china_7191154.jpg%3F20260313103832%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fserbia-buys-chinese-supersonic-missiles-13519131%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Serbia%2C%20a%20NATO%20partner%20and%20candidate%20for%20EU%20membership%2C%20has%20bought%20Chinese%20missiles%20for%20its%20air%20force.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fserbia-buys-chinese-supersonic-missiles-13519131%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20empty%20nesters%2C%20celebrating%20our%2025th%20anniversary.%20A%20trip%20to%20Japan%20was%20exactly%20what%20we%20needed%20to%20reconnect.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221923%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Erika%20Ebsworth-Goold%20and%20her%20husband%20sitting%20in%20a%20Japanese%20restuarnat%20with%20food%20in%20front%20of%20them%20on%20the%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2dd36a96e437d6eb834d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221442%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20traveled%20to%20Japan%20as%20empty%20nesters.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Erika%20Ebsworth-Goold%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20to%20Japan%20for%20our%20first%20trip%20since%20becoming%20empty%20nesters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20loved%20traveling%20the%20country%20and%20trying%20out%20new%20experiences.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20were%20able%20to%20reconnect%2C%20and%20the%20trip%20reminded%20me%20why%20I%20loved%20my%20husband%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20the%20case%20for%20many%20couples%2C%20travel%20has%20always%20been%20the%20magic%20ingredient%20that%20bonds%20my%20husband%20and%20me.%20We%20are%20both%20seekers%2C%20curious%20sorts%20bordering%20on%20downright%20nosy%2C%20so%20delving%20into%20a%20new%20destination%20is%20a%20shared%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20honeymoon%20%E2%80%94%20my%20first-ever%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountries-everyone-should-visit-from-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20we%20traipsed%20through%20Rome%2C%20Florence%2C%20and%20Venice.%20I%20was%20absolutely%20smitten.%20In%20the%20years%20since%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20criss-crossed%20the%20world%20together%2C%20with%20our%20son%20often%20in%20tow.%20But%20our%20globetrotting%20ways%20took%20a%20back%20seat%20when%20our%20kid%20started%20high%20school.%20Gone%20were%20the%20days%20we%20could%20simply%20pull%20him%20from%20classes%20for%20a%20jet-setting%20adventure%2C%20and%20he%20was%20still%20too%20young%20to%20be%20left%20home%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20son%20is%20now%20a%20college%20sophomore.%20He's%20settled%20into%20campus%20life%2C%20while%20we've%20navigated%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fempty-nest-mom-worried-daughter-lonely-siblings-moved-out-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eempty%20nest%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20we%20approached%20our%2025th%20wedding%20anniversary%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20time%20to%20get%20back%20out%20there%20in%20a%20big%20way%2C%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215e06265-6cfd-4ba8-af42-4cee2acfcdf4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20first%20had%20a%20big%20decision%20to%20make%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20we%20needed%20to%20do%20was%20decide%20on%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountries-everyone-should-add-to-bucket-list-from-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravel%20itinerary%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20became%20an%20exercise%20in%20compromise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lobbied%20for%20Morocco%3A%20visions%20of%20dreamy%20riads%2C%20the%20desert's%20golden%20light%2C%20and%20romantic%20scenes%20from%20the%20film%20%26quot%3BCasablanca%26quot%3B%20filled%20my%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20had%20another%20plan%2C%20a%20complete%20180%20from%20what%20I%20had%20in%20mind.%20Japan%20topped%20his%20list%2C%20and%20for%20all%20the%20great%20reasons%20you'd%20expect%3A%20the%20food%2C%20the%20history%2C%20the%20art%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20the%20culture.%20The%20good%20news%20is%20all%20of%20those%20things%20interest%20me%20as%20well%2C%20so%20it%20didn't%20take%20much%20to%20shift%20my%20mindset.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20immediately%20booked%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-raise-prices-cancel-flights-due-to-fuel-costs-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplane%20tickets%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Tokyo%20and%20planned%20a%20side%20trip%20to%20Kyoto.%20Morocco%20can%20wait%3B%20we'll%20get%20there%20eventually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229cf20453-1f3c-43ea-afe4-d6db535d56a8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EJapan%20was%20everything%20we%20expected%20it%20to%20be%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20marveled%20at%20the%20immersive%2C%20trippy%20art%20in%20Azabudai%20Hills%2C%20respectfully%20offered%20prayers%20at%20historic%20temples%2C%20and%20strolled%20through%20immaculate%20gardens.%20We%20savored%20an%20incredible%2014-course%20omakase%20dinner.%20We%20survived%20the%20famed%20Shibuya%20Scramble%20and%20sipped%20green-hued%20matcha-infused%20beer%20at%20the%20top%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplaces-in-japan-virtually-vs-real-life-comparison-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETokyo%20City%20View%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20fumbled%20through%20buying%20our%20Shinkansen%20tickets%20at%20a%20busy%20kiosk%2C%20marveling%20at%20the%20views%20aboard%20the%20famed%20bullet%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Erika%20Ebsworth-Goold%20in%20front%20of%20a%20temple%20arch%20in%20japan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2dd7ea96e437d6eb834ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20loved%20traveling%20throughout%20Japan.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Erika%20Ebsworth-Goold%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20of%20us%20speaks%20Japanese.%20Throughout%20our%20trip%2C%20we%20relied%20on%20each%20other%20and%20solved%20problems%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20most%20gratified%20to%20realize%20we%20still%20enjoyed%20each%20other's%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2662d99-4a2e-40bc-92d3-4a66800fadf7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20loved%20trying%20new%20experiences%20as%20empty%20nesters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20empty%20nest%20might%20make%20for%20a%20quieter%20existence%2C%20it%20doesn't%20necessarily%20change%20everyday%20household%20stress%20or%20schedules.%20Let's%20face%20it%3A%20the%20daily%20grind%20can%20become%20tedious%20even%20for%20the%20most%20committed%20couples.%20But%20our%20holiday%20restored%20the%20shine%20that%20day-to-day%20routines%20tend%20to%20dull.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drastic%20change%20of%20scenery%20Japan%20provided%20was%20a%20welcome%20jolt%2C%20giving%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20step%20far%20outside%20my%20own%20comfort%20zone%20on%20our%20final%20day.%20When%20I%20discovered%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-japan-ryokan-japanese-inn-better-than-western-hotel-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKyoto%20hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20an%20on-site%20onsen%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20dip.%20For%20the%20record%3A%20my%20husband%20declined%20the%20chance%20to%20hit%20up%20the%20men's%20facilities%2C%20but%20told%20me%20to%20go%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20tradition%2C%20bathing%20suits%20are%20not%20allowed%20in%20the%20mineral%20spring%20spas.%20I%20had%20to%20take%20the%20waters%20just%20like%20anyone%20else%2C%20in%20the%20buff.%20I'd%20successfully%20navigated%20temples%2C%20shrines%2C%20mysterious%20foods%2C%20and%20massive%20crowds.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20guess%20what%3F%20I%20survived%20the%20onsen%2C%20too%2C%20in%20the%20nude.%20No%20regrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225df1ed31-438f-4b81-8c5e-b106a064931c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20empty%20nesters%20redefined%20our%20relationship%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20come%20to%20realize%20that%20our%20empty%20nest%20is%20actually%20a%20wonderful%20opportunity.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20the%20time%20and%20freedom%20to%20redefine%20ourselves.%20The%20primary%20focus%20is%20no%20longer%20raising%20our%20child%3A%20that%20heavy%20lifting%20is%20pretty%20much%20done.%20We%20can%20now%20redirect%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20energy%20back%20to%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20has%20always%20connected%20us%20and%20refilled%20our%20collective%20tank%3B%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-full-medical-checkup-japan-how-cost-helpful-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejourney%20to%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20proof%20that%20it%20still%20does.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20all%20the%20reasons%20I%20was%20drawn%20to%20my%20husband%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20We%20remain%20a%20great%20team%2C%20especially%20on%20the%20go%2C%20half%20a%20world%20away.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperiencing%20a%20new%20place%20with%20my%20best%20friend%20is%20a%20thrill%2C%20one%20that%20allows%20us%20to%20keep%20creating%20new%20life%20chapters%20and%20memories%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20already%20itching%20to%20pack%20my%20bags%20again.%20Where%20to%20next%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fempty-nesters-rekindled-relationship-travel-japan-2026-3%5C%22%3