0Atlassian's%20repositioning%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BAI%20era.%26quot%3B%20(You%20can%20watch%20his%20four-minute%20video%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatlassian-ceo-ai-layoffs-video-message-tech-software-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexplaining%20the%20layoffs%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20comes%20a%20few%20weeks%20after%20Jack%20Dorsey%20laid%20off%2040%25%20of%20Block's%20staff%20while%20also%20pointing%20out%20that%20AI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-dorsey-block-job-cuts-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereshaped%20how%20the%20company%20could%20run%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShedding%20staff%20because%20you're%20ushering%20in%20a%20new%20era%20of%20AI%20efficiency%20is%20a%20convenient%20bit%20of%20corporate%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAtlassian's%20stock%20was%20down%20more%20than%2050%25%20this%20year%20before%20the%20layoff%20announcement%2C%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20ongoing%20SaaSpocalypse.%20Block%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20down%20more%20than%2080%25%20from%20its%202021%20highs%20when%20it%20pulled%20the%20trigger%20on%20its%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlock's%20Dorsey%20said%20blaming%20layoffs%20on%20overhiring%20during%20the%20pandemic%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-dorseys-mea-culpa-on-block-layoffs-we-overhired-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emisses%20all%20the%20complexity%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20math%20does%20look%20simple%20here%2C%20though.%20Layoffs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-make-job-cuts-worries-about-economy-and-ai-impacts-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20investors%20typically%20gobble%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20sprinkle%20of%20AI%20reinvention%20can%20also%20be%20a%20sure-fire%20way%20to%20jumpstart%20a%20company%20that's%20had%20a%20tough%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20colleague%20broke%