20recently%20announced%20layoffs%20via%20public%20memos.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBoth%20memos%20emphasized%20tech%20advancements%20and%20suggested%20the%20companies%20were%20entering%20a%20new%20era%20of%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tech%20leaders%20have%20stressed%20AI's%20impact%20on%20their%20companies%20and%20say%20business%20remains%20strong.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech%20leaders%20once%20pointed%20to%20the%20economy%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-make-job-cuts-worries-about-economy-and-ai-impacts-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecutting%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%20they%20point%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20layoff%20memos%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblock-lay-off-4000-employees-read-jack-dorseys-memo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlock%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatlassian-layoff-global-workforce-attributes-it-to-the-ai-era-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAtlassian%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20read%20less%20like%20apologetic%20explanations%20of%20economic%20headwinds%20or%20cost-cutting%20initiatives%2C%20and%20more%20like%20strategic%20manifestos%20for%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-jack-dorsey-ai-impact-as-block-cuts-layoffs-workforce-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlock's%20Jack%20Dorsey%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Atlassian's%20Mike%20Cannon-Brookes%20both%20frankly%20highlight%20profound%20shifts%20in%20how%20they%20see%20technology%20reshaping%20work%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20how%20many%20workers%20they'll%20need%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20technology%2C%20combined%20with%20smaller%20and%20flatter%20teams%2C%20Dorsey%20wrote%20in%20his%20late-February%20memo%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Benabling%20a%20new%20way%20of%20working%20which%20fundamentally%20changes%20what%20it%20means%20to%20build%20and%20run%20a%20company.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20on%20February%2026th%20that%20the%20company%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-can-show-their-ai-success-by-cutting-workers-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20its%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAtlassian%2C%20the%20software%20company%20that%20makes%20productivity%20tools%20like%20Jira%20and%20Trello%2C%20announced%20a%20cut%20of%20about%2010%25%20on%20Wednesday.%20In%20his%20memo%2C%20Cannon-Brookes%20didn't%20just%20detail%20severance%20packages%20or%20highlight%20factors%20like%20macroeconomic%20pressures%20%E2%80%94%20the%20usual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-layoffs-impact-1000-workers-ceo-memo-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efodder%20of%20such%20missives%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20instead%20laid%20out%20the%20company's%20AI%20philosophy%20and%20how%20it%20was%20restructuring%20in%20response%2C%20using%20boldface%20for%20emphasis%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20fundamentally%20believe%20people%20%3Cstrong%3Eand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20AI%20create%20the%20best%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stepped-up%20focus%20on%20where%20companies%20need%20to%20go%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20the%20economic%20constraints%20that%20might%20have%20led%20them%20to%20make%20the%20cuts%20%E2%80%94%20is%20new%2C%20Rick%20Wargo%2C%20managing%20partner%20and%20global%20technology%20practice%20leader%20at%20the%20executive%20search%20firm%20Boyden%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20things%20have%20progressed%2C%20they've%20come%20to%20realize%20that%20different%20skills%20are%20needed%20than%20perhaps%20what%20they%20hired%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20business%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d0b9e55-651e-43d9-8cfc-7d8688c5ed10%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20AI%20era%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20other%20leaders%20have%20also%20cited%20AI's%20impact%20when%20making%20cuts%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-reality-labs-vr-horizon-worlds-teams-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangi-layoffs-angies-list-cuts-350-jobs-ai-efficiency-gains-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAngi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2026%23wise-tech-is-cutting-30-of-its-workforce-18%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWiseTech%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20June%2C%20Amazon's%20Andy%20Jassy%20wrote%20that%20the%20company's%20AI%20push%20would%20mean%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-employees-criticize-ceo-jassys-ai-driven-job-cutting-plan-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany's%20corporate%20workforce%20would%20shrink%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20in%20subsequent%20reductions%2C%20Amazon%20identified%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-new-layoffs-restructuring-continues-cultural-reset-andy-jassy-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eneed%20for%20a%20cultural%20reset%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Dorsey%20and%20Cannon-Brookes%20said%20the%20cuts%20aren't%20a%20symptom%20of%20an%20ailing%20business%20and%20used%20their%20layoff%20memos%20to%20make%20the%20case%20for%20their%20visions%20for%20their%20respective%20companies%20in%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enew%20AI%20age.%20Dorsey%3Cstrong%3E%3Cs%3E%20%3C%2Fs%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20that%20the%20company's%20profitability%20is%20improving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20CFO%20also%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20call%20that%2C%20because%20of%20AI%2C%20the%20code%20each%20of%20its%20engineers%20ships%20has%20increased%20by%20more%20than%2040%25%20since%20September.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20engineering%20work%20that%20would%20have%20taken%20weeks%20to%20complete%20be%20done%20by%20a%20small%20team%20in%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20time%20with%20agentic%20coding%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amrita%20Ahuja%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20company's%20COO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Atlassian%2C%20Cannon-Brookes%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20momentum.%26quot%3B%20He%20went%20on%20to%20highlight%20gains%20in%20cloud%20revenue%20and%20other%20metrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELayoff%20memos%20often%20highlight%20a%20company's%20strength%20and%20stability.%20These%20latest%20notes%20go%20further%20than%20some%20by%20outlining%20leadership's%20priorities%20for%20those%20who%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECannon-Brookes%20framed%20Atlassian's%20cutbacks%20as%20being%20about%20adaptation%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20reshaping%20our%20skill%20mix%20and%20changing%20how%20we%20work%20to%20build%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c68e65cc-cd9f-4ddf-ac11-11143ed117b0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20limits%20of%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-laying-off-workers-in-waves-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewaves%20of%20tech%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20has%20been%20much%20discussion%20about%20whether%20AI%20is%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-make-job-cuts-worries-about-economy-and-ai-impacts-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroot%20of%20these%20reductions%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20when%20it's%20explicitly%20framed%20that%20way.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAI%20likely%20doesn't%20account%20for%20all%20the%20layoffs%20tech%20companies%20are%20making%2C%20Will%20Wilson%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Antithesis%2C%20an%20autonomous%20software-testing%20platform%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20growing%20companies%20have%20stopped%20hiring%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Wilson%20said%20that%20as%20AI%20improves%2C%20the%20chance%20it%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-secure-job-in-tech-block-layoffs-ai-warning-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereplace%20workers%20increases%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20technology%20provided%20little%2C%20if%20any%2C%20productivity%20benefit%20to%20most%20people%2C%20Wilson%20said.%20Now%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it's%20clearly%20offering%20some%20efficiency%20windfall%20in%20areas%20like%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20there%20are%20limits%20to%20how%20much%20companies%20that%20go%20big%20on%20AI%20will%20be%20able%20to%20cut%2C%20said%20Josh%20Bersin%2C%20CEO%20of%20The%20Josh%20Bersin%20Company%2C%20a%20consulting%20firm.%20AI%20can%20automate%20something%20like%20code%20generation%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20eliminate%20the%20need%20for%20workers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20check%20the%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20Bersin%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BYou%20still%20have%20to%20test%20it.%20You%20still%20have%20to%20update%20it.%20You%20still%20have%20to%20maintain%20it.%20You%20still%20need%20to%20do%20the%20production%20management.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20the%20debate%20over%20how%20much%20AI%20is%20driving%20the%20cuts%20versus%20just%20age-old%20business%20imperatives%2C%20some%20leaders%20are%20using%20layoff%20announcements%20to%20lay%20out%20their%20vision%20for%20how%20their%20companies%20will%20navigate%20this%20new%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECannon-Brookes%20ended%20his%20message%20by%20saying%20that%20Atlassian%20had%20navigated%20multiple%20tech%20shifts%20and%20market%20cycles%20%E2%80%94%20and%20thrived%20while%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20require%20continual%20adaptation.%20Decisiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20making%20hard%20decisions%20to%20set%20Atlassian%20up%20strongly%20for%20the%20long%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoff-announcement-memos-are-ai-era-strategy-manifestos-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773395702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b339ef4d65ec517529f080%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoff-announcement-memos-are-ai-era-strategy-manifestos-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20CEOs%20once%20blamed%20the%20economy%20for%20layoffs.%20Now%20leaders%20at%20firms%20including%20Block%20and%20Atlassian%20say%20AI%20is%20reshaping%20work%20%E2%80%94%20and%20shrinking%20teams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoff-announcement-memos-are-ai-era-strategy-manifestos-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20dietitian's%20favorite%20quick%2C%20high-protein%20recipes%2C%20including%20the%20turkey%20skillet%20she%20makes%20every%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachael%20DeVaux%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aee417fd4fbd083f29c1d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachael%20DeVaux%2C%20a%20registered%20dietitian%2C%20shared%20recipes%20from%20her%20cookbook%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20High-Protein%20Plate.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEva%20Kolenko%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERachael%20DeVaux%20is%20a%20registered%20dietitian%20specializing%20in%20protein-forward%20meals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20High-Protein%20Plate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20shared%20a%20few%20of%20her%20favorite%20recipes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOvernight%20oats%2C%20chicken%20salad%2C%20and%20a%2030-minute%20turkey%20skillet%20are%20her%20favorite%20quick%2C%20high-protein%20meals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEating%20enough%20protein%20doesn't%20mean%20living%20on%20dry%20chicken%20and%20shakes%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20DeVaux%2C%20a%20registered%20dietitian%20who%20aims%20to%20eat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-100-grams-protein-a-day-dietitian-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E100%20grams%20of%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20day%2C%20finds%20it%20easier%20to%20stick%20to%20your%20protein%20goals%20when%20you%20actually%20enjoy%20your%20dinners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20healthy%20eating%20to%20feel%20boring%2C%20or%20for%20people%20to%20think%20that%20they%20have%20to%20eat%20plain%20chicken%20and%20broccoli%20for%20every%20meal%2C%26quot%3B%20DeVaux%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20High-Protein%20Plate%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20common%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20to%20get%20between%200.5%20and%200.7%20grams%20of%20protein%20per%20pound%20of%20body%20weight%20each%20day%2C%20adjusted%20for%20goals%20like%20muscle%20gain%20or%20fat%20loss.%20For%20a%20person%20who%20weighs%20150%20pounds%2C%20that%20breaks%20down%20to%20about%2025%20to%2035%20grams%20per%20meal%20when%20eating%20three%20times%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeVaux%20likes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-high-protein-trader-joes-sheet-pan-dinner-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprep%20a%20few%20protein%20sources%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20week%20(like%20grilled%20chicken%20breasts%20or%20hard-boiled%20eggs)%20as%20well%20as%20a%20few%20sauces%20(such%20as%20homemade%20pesto%20or%20a%20dijon-and-olive%20oil%20vinaigrette).%20Bases%20like%20quinoa%2C%20farro%2C%20or%20rice%20noodles%20can%20also%20be%20cooked%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20easy%20to%20throw%20together%20a%20quick%20meal%20if%20you%20have%20just%20veggies%20in%20the%20fridge%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20as%20those%20can%20take%2010%20to%2015%20minutes%20to%20cook.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20how%20I%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20meals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20has%20a%20few%20recipes%20she%20leans%20on%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-costco-high-protein-foods-from-athlete-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equick%20high-protein%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20DeVaux%20shared%20three%20of%20her%20favorites%20from%20her%20new%20cookbook%2C%20including%20the%20full%20recipe%20for%20a%2030-minute%20turkey%20skillet%20she%20makes%20every%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec592ac7-99d2-4ad5-b2bb-8d0006bbfd8d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHoney-blackberry%20overnight%20oats%20pack%20in%20the%20protein%20and%20fiber%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachael%20DeVaux%20making%20overnight%20oats%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aee58afd4fbd083f29c203%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeVaux%20makes%20honey-blackberry%20overnight%20oats%20that%20clock%20in%20at%2035%20grams%20of%20protein%2C%20thanks%20to%20extra%20ingredients%20like%20Greek%20yogurt%20and%20nuts.%3Cp%3EEva%20Kolenko%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDeVaux%20loves%20prepping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-breakfast-weight-loss-recipe-protein-fiber-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eovernight%20oats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20takes%20away%20that%20decision%20fatigue%20of%20what%20to%20make%20for%20breakfast%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20grab%20it%20as%20you're%20running%20out%20the%20door%2C%20but%20it's%20full%20of%20protein%2C%20and%20it%20keeps%20you%20satiated%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20makes%20a%20honey-blackberry%2