www.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-finland-trains-nato-arctic-warfare-snowmobiles-skis-lasers-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EArctic%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20takes%20on%20greater%20significance%20for%20the%20US%20and%20its%20NATO%20allies%2C%20it%20is%20increasingly%20critical%20to%20know%20firsthand%20how%20to%20fight%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-troops-cant-let-guns-get-too-warm-frozen-battlefields-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efrozen%20battlefields%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20Carolina%20can't%20mirror%20the%20conditions%20in%20Norway%2C%20Sweden%2C%20and%20Finland%20above%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%2C%20said%20Col.%20William%20Soucie%2C%20the%2010th%20Marine%20Regiment%20commanding%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20almost%20no%20way%20to%20replicate%20the%20elements%2C%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20test%20the%20equipment%20the%20way%20in%20which%20we're%20able%20to%20do%20it%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Soucie%20told%20Business%20Insider%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20firing%20range%20in%20Setermoen%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22US%20Marines%20fire%20HIMARS%20rockets%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FTQjSltAd-rpoASVKQ.html%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ELong-range%20precision%20fires%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-proving-ground-for-newest-us-weapons-missile-drone-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHIMARS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20M142%20High%20Mobility%20Artillery%20Rocket%20System%2C%20have%20proven%20their%20worth%20in%20multiple%20conflicts%2C%20including%20Ukraine%2C%20used%20by%20Kyiv%20to%20hit%20key%20Russian%20targets%20well%20behind%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20Moscow's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-war-chernobyl-ukraine-most-radioactive-place-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efull-scale%20invasion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20allies%20have%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20HIMARS'%20successes%20in%20Ukraine.%20Estonia%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20said%20in%202025%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-member-estonia-doubling-down-us-made-himars-ukraine-success-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuy%20more%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20received%20several%20earlier%20in%20the%20year%3B%20more%20recently%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20said%20it%20approved%20the%20sale%20of%2020%20to%20Sweden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHIMARS%2C%20like%20other%20systems%20that%20can%20fire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-rocket-system-packing-twice-punch-himars-fired-first-time-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprecision-guided%20rocket%20artillery%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20missiles%20over%20vast%20distances%2C%20would%20be%20critical%20assets%20in%20any%20future%20conflict%20in%20the%20Arctic%2C%20which%20often%20features%20open%2C%20rolling%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20nasty%20weather%20up%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20First%20Lt.%20Landon%20Foster%2C%20the%20HIMARS%20platoon%20commander%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20snows%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20aircraft%20can't%20always%20come%20in%20in%20low-visibility%20conditions%2C%20which%20you%20experience%20during%20snowstorms%20and%20whatnot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HIMARS%2C%20Foster%20said%2C%20allows%20Marines%20to%20deliver%20effects%20similar%20to%20what%20those%20aircraft%20can%20do%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhen%20conditions%20make%20using%20the%20latter%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2