6quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22US%20Marines%20train%20in%20winter%20conditions%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FHaOBagq8-rpoASVKQ.html%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20real%20combat%20scenarios%2C%20commanders%20acknowledge%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-try-cut-russia-supply-chains-winter-freeze-them-out-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupply%20and%20logistics%20chains%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20become%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20Marines.%20The%20terrain%20is%20notoriously%20difficult%20to%20navigate%2C%20and%20moving%20ammunition%20or%20fuel%20requires%20large%2C%20reliable%20vehicles%20that%20can%20survive%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20look%20throughout%20history%20and%20see%20examples%20of%20where%20logistics%20has%20been%20a%20challenge%20in%20environments%20like%20this%2C%20and%20I%20would%20say%20that%20would%20probably%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20us%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Foster%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20the%20Marines%20are%20practicing%20in%20Setermoen%20is%20ensuring%20that%20they%20have%20reliable%20access%20to%20maintenance%2C%20ammunition%2C%20and%20communications%20to%20support%20artillery's%20main%20role%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-general-artillery-must-be-mobile-spread-out-survive-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efiring%20in%20support%20of%20maneuver%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20harder%20above%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%20because%20it's%20colder%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Soucie%2C%20the%20Marine%20colonel.%20%26quot%3BHuman%20reactions%20are%20slower%3B%20machine%2