d%20depreciation%20of%20the%20rupee%20against%20the%20euro%2C%20along%20with%20rising%20input%20costs%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fafter-audi-mercedes-to-hike-prices-by-2-from-april-amid-forex-volatility-126031300562_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fafter-audi-mercedes-to-hike-prices-by-2-from-april-amid-forex-volatility-126031300562_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fafter-audi-mercedes-to-hike-prices-by-2-from-april-amid-forex-volatility-126031300562_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top-2%25%20fund%20manager%20shares%20where%20he'll%20be%20looking%20for%20opportunities%20as%20Middle%20East%20turmoil%20threatens%20tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22oil%20storage%20facilities%20targeted%2C%20including%20the%20Shehran%20oil%20depot%2C%20in%20Tehran%2C%20Iran%20on%20March%208%2C%202026%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ae0b2fd3e2f1aef36a33c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERising%20oil%20prices%20due%20to%20the%20Iran%20war%20could%20impact%20tech%20stocks%20and%20the%20AI%20trade.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20according%20to%20Tom%20Hancock%2C%20a%20fund%20manager%20at%20GMO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20suggested%20looking%20to%20healthcare%20stocks%20if%20Middle%20East%20turmoil%20continues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-100-iran-war-tanker-attacks-hormuz-reserve-release-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERising%20oil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20potential%20impact%20on%20inflation%20%E2%80%94%20are%20front%20and%20center%20in%20the%20market%20conversation%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20if%20the%20conflict%20between%20Iran%20and%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20continues%20and%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20stays%20closed%2C%20attention%20could%20start%20to%20shift%20to%20the%20tech%20sector%20and%20the%20AI%20trade%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-stock-picks-to-buy-now-etf-innovators-gmo-tema-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETom%20Hancock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Focused%20Equity%20team%20at%20asset%20management%20firm%20GMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20may%20seem%20like%20an%20odd%20line%20to%20draw%20at%20first%2C%20Hancock%20is%20thinking%20of%20the%20potential%20knock-on%20effects%20on%20capital%20flows%20that%20could%20stem%20from%20an%20extended%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fships-come-under-fire-around-the-strait-of-hormuz-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclosure%20of%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Middle%20Eastern%20oil%20producers%20can't%20easily%20sell%20their%20oil%20in%20the%20global%20market%2C%20they%20have%20less%20money%20coming%20in%20to%20invest%20in%20US%20assets.%20This%20could%20be%20particularly%20harmful%20to%20tech%20companies%2C%20he%20said%2C%20which%20are%20borrowing%20heavily%20to%20fund%20AI%20data%20centers%20and%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20buy%20their%20oil%2C%20money%20goes%20in%2C%20that%20money%20comes%20out%2C%20and%20it%20goes%20into%20things%20like%20data%20centers%20and%20private%20equity%20and%20venture%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20Hancock%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20adding%20that%20a%20risk-off%20shift%20could%20lead%20to%20less%20investment%20from%20the%20region%2C%20which%20makes%20him%20concerned%20about%20the%20continued%20foreign%20investment%20into%20the%20tech%20space.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHancock%20said%20the%20effects%20could%20hit%20tech%20manufacturers%20by%20raising%20energy%20costs%2C%20too.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20things%20would%20have%20to%20be%20pretty%20severe%20before%20TSMC%20was%20on%20course%20not%20to%20run%20their%20fabs%2C%20but%20it%20could%20at%20least%20hit%20their%20profit%20margins.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20danger%20of%20such%20a%20scenario%20playing%20out%20is%20not%20necessarily%20imminent%2C%20Hancock%20said%2C%20as%20the%20blockade%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20would%20have%20to%20last%20months%20to%20result%20in%20heavily%20curtailed%20investment%20flows%20from%20the%20region.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20prolonged%20blockade%20now%20appears%20to%20be%20at%20least%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20playing%20out.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20oil%20prices%20surged%20back%20to%20%24100%20as%20Iran's%20new%20Supreme%20Leader%2C%20Mojtaba%20Khamenei%2C%20said%20that%20the%20country%20would%20continue%20to%20keep%20the%20critical%20shipping%20lane%20shuttered.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221da6e5f0-0033-4a6f-8ceb-2732f3e73640%5C%22%3EWhere%20to%20hide%20if%20Middle%20East%20turmoil%20continues%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHancock%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20investing%20during%20volatile%20times.%20In%20fact%2C%20his%20GMO%20Quality%20Fund%2C%20which%20Morningstar%20data%20shows%20has%20beaten%2098%25%20of%20similar%20funds%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20is%20built%20to%20weather%20market%20storms%20by%20focusing%20on%20stocks%20with%20strong%20business%20models%20and%20high%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20would%20he%20shift%20his%20strategy%20if%20turmoil%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20continues%20to%20shake%20financial%20markets%3F%20He%20said%20he'd%20ramp%20up%20his%20allocation%20to%20the%20healthcare%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20were%20getting%20more%20risk-averse%2C%20that's%20probably%20where%20we%20would%20be%20deploying%20more%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHealthcare%20is%20traditionally%20considered%20a%20defensive%20sector%2C%20meaning%20it%20tends%20to%20be%20insulated%20from%20fluctuations%20in%20the%20business%20cycle.%20But%20Hancock%20said%20it's%20also%20attractive%20on%20a%20secular%2C%20fundamental%20basis%2C%20and%20called%20it%20one%20of%20the%20best%20opportunities%20in%20the%20market%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20especially%20likes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Funh-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUnitedHealth%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnited%20Health%20Group%20can%20be%20very%20volatile%20about%20whatever%20news%20is%20coming%20out%20of%20CMS%20and%20US%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20Hancock%20said%2C%20using%20the%20acronym%20for%20the%20Centers%20for%20Medicare%20and%20Medicaid%20Services.%20%26quot%3BSo%20depending%20on%20what%20the%20news%20flow%20is%2C%20that's%20actually%20when%20those%20kind%20of%20companies%20tend%20to%20do%20best%2C%20when%20no%20one's%20talking%20about%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20investors%20seeking%20broader%20exposure%20to%20the%20healthcare%20sector%2C%20examples%20of%20relevant%20exchange-traded%20funds%20include%20the%20State%20Street%20Health%20Care%20Select%20Sector%20SPDR%20ETF%20(XLV)%20and%20the%20iShares%20US%20Healthcare%20ETF%20(IYH).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-stock-market-strategy-iran-war-oil-prices-surging-gmo-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773393301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b31adda7a4f9df67ba4214%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-stock-market-strategy-iran-war-oil-prices-surging-gmo-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rising%20oil%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20potential%20impact%20on%20inflation%20%E2%80%94%20are%20front%20and%20center%20for%20markets%2C%20but%20the%20Iran%20war%20could%20soon%20hit%20tech.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-stock-market-strategy-iran-war-oil-prices-surging-gmo-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20run%20an%20AI-powered%20startup%2C%20and%20we%20canceled%20our%20ChatGPT%20business%20plan%20months%20ago.%20Claude%20feels%20more%20like%20the%20promise%20of%20AI.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22893%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smiling%20man%20with%20shoulder-length%20dark%20hair%20and%20cross%20earrings%20wears%20a%20navy%20blazer%20and%20white%20shirt%20in%20an%20indoor%20office%20setting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2ed914d65ec517529e8c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESidhant%20Bendre%20canceled%20his%20ChatGPT%20business%20plan%20for%20Claude.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sidhant%20Bendre%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESidhant%20Bendre%20canceled%20his%20AI%20startup's%20ChatGPT%20subscription%20and%20switched%20to%20Claude%20last%20fall.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20Claude's%20model%20reduces%20coding%20errors%20and%20mimics%20human%20writing%20better%20than%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20remains%20open%20to%20switching%20back%20or%20to%20a%20new%20model%20if%20something%20better%20comes%20along.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sidhant%20Bendre%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20cofounder%20of%20Oleve%2C%20an%20AI-driven%20consumer%20software%20portfolio%20company%2C%20based%20in%20New%20York.%20His%20words%20have%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20ChatGPT%20for%20roughly%20two%20years%20before%20moving%20over%20to%20Claude%20as%20my%20preferred%20model%20and%20ending%20my%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-number-1-app-stores-chatgpt-apple-google-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20subscription%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-company-hires-tiny-team-machine-learning-engineers-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eour%20company%2C%20Oleve%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20were%20already%20using%20AI%2C%20so%20we've%20always%20relied%20heavily%20on%20it%20in%20our%20workflow%2C%20from%20coding%20to%20marketing%20to%20our%20hiring%20process.%20ChatGPT%20was%20our%20go-to%20model.%20After%20Anthropic%20released%20its%204.5%20model%20suite%20for%20Claude%20last%20fall%2C%20that%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20weren't%20pushed%20away%20from%20ChatGPT%3B%20we%20were%20pulled%20into%20Claude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be1f4645-e6a6-42bf-881d-d7076ea05b0b%5C%22%3ERight%20off%20the%20bat%2C%20Claude%20had%20fewer%20bugs%20generating%20code%20than%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20have%20any%20major%20frustrations%20with%20ChatGPT%20that%20forced%20us%20to%20switch%2C%20but%20I%20think%20one%20of%20the%20promises%20of%20AI%20is%20to%20speed%20up%20our%20work%2C%20and%20Claude%20let%20us%20move%20faster%20because%20we%20spent%20less%20time%20correcting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20were%20primarily%20using%20ChatGPT%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20the%20content%20it%20generated%20didn't%20sound%20very%20human.%20It%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-millennial-cringe-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoveruse%20emojis%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20I%20wouldn't%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20really%20forced.%20I%20haven't%20used%20ChatGPT%20rigorously%20for%20a%20while%20now%2C%20but%20whenever%20I%20go%20back%20to%20test%20prompts%20with%20the%20model%2C%20I%20still%20get%20those%20overly%20verbose%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaude%20is%20better%20at%20mimicking%20human%20writing.%20Even%20before%20Claude's%204.5%20suite%20came%20out%2C%20we'd%20heard%20students%20talk%20about%20how%20the%20model%20was%20so%20good%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-doubled-income-save-me-fifteen-hours-each-week-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emimicking%20their%20writing%20style%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20they%20fed%20it%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-outages-anthropic-ai-software-engineers-developers-coding-dependance-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude's%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20automate%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20development%20time%20with%20blueprints%20we%20already%20had.%20Now%20we%20can%20focus%20more%20on%20the%20product%20itself%20rather%20than%20spending%20so%20much%20energy%20on%20build%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22693725d4-362f-476b-a5d4-69c6d3e2b9c8%5C%22%3EThe%20way%20the%20models%20understand%20nuance%20is%20the%20biggest%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20difference%20between%20the%20models%20seems%20to%20be%20parsing%20context%20and%20considering%20nuance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20feed%20Claude%20a%20large%20research%20document%20and%20I'm%20looking%20for%20something%20small%2C%20it%20almost%20always%20understands%20when%20to%20be%20concise%2C%20while%20providing%20the%20appropriate%20context%20and%20highlighting%20what%20I'm%20asking%20for%20more%20details%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20it%20felt%20like%20ChatGPT%20was%20overcompensating%20for%20poor%20judgment%20about%20what%20to%20focus%20on%20by%20spitting%20out%20more%20content.%20If%20I'm%20using%20it%20at%20all%20now%2C%20I%20usually%20have%20to%20ask%20it%20multiple%20times%20to%20summarize%20or%20reinstruct%20it%20to%20be%20more%20concise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwielding-the-power-of-ai-how-solopreneurs-streamline-their-workflow-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintegrated%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20more%20of%20our%20workflows%20after%20switching%20to%20Claude.%20It%20made%20more%20sense%20to%20invest%20the%20time%20and%20energy%20it%20takes%20to%20do%20that%20when%20I%20know%20the%20payoff%20is%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f857caf-862e-4d70-9d32-5a11f66f3e8c%5C%22%3EClaude%20has%20given%20us%20its%20own%20set%20of%20problems%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Claude%20has%20been%20giving%20us%20its%20own%20set%20of%20issues%20with%20bugginess.%20Some%20of%20our%20messages%20or%20chats%20have%20been%20disappearing%2C%20and%20this%20has%20been%20frustrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20perfect.%20I%20feel%20like%20there%20are%20still%20hallucinations%20I%20see%20in%20the%20model's%20output%20every%20now%20and%20then%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20my%20trust%20in%20Claude%20crumble%20a%20little%20bit.%20I%20have%20to%20push%20back%20in%20these%20scenarios%20to%20self-correct%2C%20even%20with%20web%20search%20on%20their%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-openai-rivalry-dueling-ai-models-on-the-same-day-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpus%204.6%20model%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8e16cc6-776b-4e47-85bb-a653f1790ad8%5C%22%3EI'm%20still%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20Claude's%20suite%2C%20but%20if%20something%20better%20comes%20along%2C%20I'd%20switch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20haven't%20really%20been%20paying%20attention%20to%20the%20larger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-dario-amodei-anthropic-openai-rivalry-timeline-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20vs%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20debate.%20If%20ChatGPT%20launches%20a%20product%20suite%20that%20provides%20significant%20value%20to%20me%2C%20I%20would%20try%20it.%20I%20don't%20feel%20attached%20to%20Claude%20to%20the%20point%20where%20I%20wouldn't%20try%20something%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20the%20biggest%20thing%20for%20me%20has%20been%20that%20Claude%20feels%20so%20much%20more%20like%20what%20the%20promise%20of%20AI%20is%20supposed%20to%20be.%20All%20the%20models%20have%20provided%20significant%20value%2C%20but%20it%20feels%20a%20lot%20more%20like%20it's%20taking%20away%20the%20busywork%20from%20my%20day-to-day%20and%20giving%20me%20back%20time%20to%20think%20big%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20using%20AI%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%2C%20Agnes%20Applegate%2C%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ai-startup-founder-switched-chatgpt-to-claude-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773393061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2ed9da96e437d6eb83712%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ai-startup-founder-switched-chatgpt-to-claude-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20AI%20startup%20cofounder%20explains%20their%20switch%20from%20ChatGPT%20to%20Claude%2C%20highlighting%20better%20nuance%20understanding%20and%20reduced%20coding%20errors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aapplegate%40insider.com%20(Agnes%20Applegate)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ai-startup-founder-switched-chatgpt-to-claude-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Andrew%20Yang%20says%20we%20should%20stop%20taxing%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20start%20taxing%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225039%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrew%20Yang%20at%20bitcoin%20conference%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F