-collar%20jobs%20within%20the%20next%20five%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20Amodei's%20suggestion%20that%20AI%20firms%20themselves%20should%20be%20taxed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20when%20does%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20major%20company%20raise%20his%20hand%20and%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20tax%20me%20and%20mine'%3F%26quot%3B%20Yang%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20tech%20leaders%20%26quot%3Bsee%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%26quot%3B%20and%20understand%20a%20backlash%20could%20be%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4429410-f15f-4594-8087-d777382edb76%5C%22%3EAn%20AI%20inflection%20point%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYang's%20call%20comes%20as%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20announced%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20layoffs%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20with%20many%20executives%20citing%20AI-driven%20restructuring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20AI-related%20layoffs%20include%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatlassian-layoff-global-workforce-attributes-it-to-the-ai-era-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E1%2C600-person%20job%20cut%20at%20Atlassian%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%2C%20due%20to%20what%20its%20CEO%20described%20as%20a%20broader%20effort%20to%20reposition%20the%20business%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BAI%20era.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Yang%2C%20those%20moves%20are%20just%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20came%20from%20an%20AI%20conference%20out%20west%2C%20and%20holy%20cow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20said%20to%20me%20that%20what%20we're%20going%20to%20see%20in%20the%20next%20six%20months%20outstrips%20what%20we've%20seen%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20AI%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20one%20company%20that%20is%20selling%20auton