B%20Yang%20told%20CNBC.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-yang-says-stop-taxing-workers-start-taxing-ai-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773393001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2d744a96e437d6eb8338f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-yang-says-stop-taxing-workers-start-taxing-ai-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere%20is%20zero%20chance%20that%20this%20transition%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20rough%20for%20millions%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Yang%20said%20of%20the%20shift%20toward%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-yang-says-stop-taxing-workers-start-taxing-ai-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Satellite%20images%2C%20tanker%20tracking%2C%20and%20prediction%20markets%3A%20The%20data%20hedge%20funds%20are%20using%20to%20invest%20during%20a%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227030%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bird's-eye%20view%20of%20an%20aerial%20attack%20by%20the%20US%20in%20Iran%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b190674d65ec517529d2b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224950%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESatellite%20images%20of%20strikes%20from%20data%20companies%20like%20Vantor%20are%20being%20used%20by%20hedge%20funds.%3Cp%3EVantor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHedge%20funds%20are%20desperate%20for%20intel%20about%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20strikes%20on%20Iran%20by%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20have%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20global%20markets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EData%20intelligence%20firm%20Neudata%20sent%20a%20rundown%20of%20vendors%20that%20could%20provide%20on-the-ground%20info.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20smart%20money%20needs%20to%20get%20smarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHedge%20funds%20and%20other%20savvy%20investors%20have%20battled%20volatile%20markets%20since%20March's%20onset%2C%20due%20to%20the%20conflict%20between%20Iran%20and%20the%20US%20and%20Israel.%20It%20has%20thrown%20interest%20rates%2C%20equities%2C%20and%20commodities%20into%20disarray%2C%20and%20many%20big-name%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrevan-howard-taula-pimco-performance-money-iran-market-turbulence-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanagers%20suffered%20losses%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20month's%20first%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20funds%20hungry%20for%20on-the-ground%20intel%20about%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20alternative%20data%20intelligence%20firm%20Neudata%20has%20compiled%20a%20report%20for%20the%20data%20consumers%20on%20its%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20think%20hedge%20funds%20and%20big%20institutional%20investors%20%E2%80%94%20outlining%20datasets%20that%20could%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESophisticated%20money%20managers%20have%20long%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-spending-on-alternative-data-jumps-2025-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emined%20obscure%20datasets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20anonymized%20credit%20card%20receipts%2C%20to%20gain%20an%20edge%20in%20the%20industries%20they%20cover.%20This%20desire%20for%20under-the-radar%20info%20also%20extends%20to%20geopolitical%20events%20that%20impact%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20products%20recommended%20by%20Neudata%20come%20from%20big-name%20data%20providers%20such%20as%20S%26amp%3BP%2C%20FreightWaves%2C%20and%20Kpler.%20Business%20Insider%20is%20highlighting%2010%20providers%2C%20mostly%20smaller%20players%2C%20that%20specialize%20in%20obscure%20data%20niches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%2010%20datasets%20Neudata%20tagged%20for%20clients%20desperate%20to%20understand%20%26quot%3Bthe%20conflict's%20current%20events%20and%20its%20potential%20broader%20global%20impacts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc88e2fa-f722-4736-a3c2-71681acd9c5a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESatellite%20players%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatellite-images-airstrikes-turn-iran-fleet-vintage-f-14s-wreckage-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESatellite%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20used%20by%20hedge%20funds%20for%20years%20to%20get%20more%20granular%20information%20on%20companies'%20health.%20Analysts%20would%20track%20the%20number%20of%20cars%20in%20parking%20lots%20at%20big%20retailers%20to%20help%20project%20next%20quarter's%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20these%20images%20are%20being%20used%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20damage%20to%20energy%20production%20sites%20caused%20by%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVendors%20such%20as%20%3Cstrong%3EVantor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EPlanet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3ESatellogic%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewere%20flagged%20by%20Neudata.%20Images%20of%20strikes%20and%20their%20damage%20can%20also%20help%20combat%20disinformation%2C%20the%20report%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20satellite%20vendors%20that%20use%20a%20technology%20known%20as%20synthetic%20aperture%20radar%2C%20which%20is%20not%20blocked%20by%20clouds%20or%20darkness.%20This%20technology%20is%20mostly%20used%20to%20track%20movement%20during%20nighttime%2C%20such%20as%20military%20vehicles%20leaving%20a%20base%2C%20and%20providers%20in%20this%20space%20include%20%3Cstrong%3EICEYE%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20%3Cstrong%3EUmbra%20Space%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b7684c7-e4a4-4964-b1a6-5f5afe2f6274%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETranspo%20trackers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20the%20narrow%20stretch%20of%20water%20between%20Iran%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20has%20become%20the%20most%20closely%20watched%20region%20in%20the%20world%20as%20the%20conflict%20continues.%20Tens%20of%20millions%20of%20barrels%20of%20crude%20oil%20pass%20through%20the%20area%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20investors%20looking%20to%20track%20how%20the%20conflict%20has%20disrupted%20shipping%20routes%20and%20trade%20patterns%2C%20Neudata%20pointed%20to%20datasets%20offered%20by%20tanker%20trackers%20%3Cstrong%3EVesselsValue%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20%3Cstrong%3ELinerlytica%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Neudata's%20report%20states%20that%2033%20hedge%20funds%20use%20VesselsValue%20data%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EFlightRadar24%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecan%20give%20macro%20investors%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20on-the-ground%20atmosphere%20in%20surrounding%20countries%20like%20the%20UAE%20and%20Qatar%20by%20providing%20information%20on%20airport%20closures%20and%20departures%20leaving%20once-safe%20havens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b16e33d6-3170-45c1-b54e-c35604a02e39%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrediction%20market%20signals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%20like%20Polymarket%20and%20Kalshi%20have%20generated%20plenty%20of%20controversy%20thanks%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkhamenei-prediction-markets-kalshi-polymarket-insider-trading-outrage-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20potential%20insider%20trading%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20platforms%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20first%20Iran%20strikes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20extraction%20of%20Venezuelan%20President%20Nicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHedge%20funds%20have%20already%20been%20tapping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-hedge-funds-are-using-prediction-markets-data-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edifferent%20data%20feeds%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20track%20prediction%20market%20activity%2C%20but%20for%20funds%20focused%20on%20the%20Middle%20East%20in%20particular%2C%20Neudata%20highlights%20a%20pair%20of%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnusual%