20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believed%20being%20in%20Seattle%20would%20offer%20more%20networking%20opportunities%2C%20and%20that%20listing%20a%20Seattle%20address%20on%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20could%20boost%20my%20chances%20with%20local%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-companies-us-linkedin-list-career-growth-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eemployers%20like%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20signaling%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20hit%20the%20ground%20running%20without%20any%20relocation%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20a%20cold%20application%20turned%20into%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-amazon-hiring-manager-looks-for-tech-interview-candidates-preparation-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20senior%20risk%20analyst%20role.%20I%20eventually%20landed%20the%20job%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20joined%20Amazon%20in%20July%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20speaking%20with%20workers%20who've%20found%20themselves%20at%20a%20corporate%20crossroads%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20due%20to%20a%20layoff%2C%20resignation%2C%20job%20search%2C%20or%20shifting%20workplace%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShare%20your%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSechTVqVWQve8iqYssNriCXdtwwdgGRixNNZpmslSKBQqIJ8g%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20contacting%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20via%20Signal%20at%20jzinkula.29.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230c7c659-792a-47e7-a330-2dd9036fa2c3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20prioritized%20living%20close%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20expected%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-5-day-rto-mandate-policy-employees-experiences-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20from%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20but%20my%20commute%20is%20very%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20landed%20the%20job%20at%20Amazon%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20South%20Lake%20Union.%20It's%20a%20neighborhood%20in%20Seattle%20where%20it%20sometimes%20feels%20like%20you%20can%20only%20find%20two%20types%20of%20people%20in%20an%20apartment%20building%3A%20Amazon%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-web-services-office-redmond-microsoft-hq-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20roommate%20and%20I%20split%20a%20rent%20of%20%244%2C800%20a%20month%2C%20including%20parking%2C%20for%20our%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20was%20only%20a%20five-minute%20walk%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20moved%20into%20my%20own%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20South%20Lake%20Union%2C%20which%20is%20a%20seven-minute%20walk%20away%20from%20my%20office.%20The%20rent%20is%20about%20%242%2C700%20a%20month%2C%20including%20parking.%20I%20found%20some%20cheaper%20options%20that%20were%20farther%20away%2C%20but%20staying%20close%20to%20the%20office%20was%20one%20of%20my%20biggest%20priorities%20while%20apartment%20hunting%20to%20avoid%20unnecessary%20travel%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20commute%20has%20allowed%20me%20to%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-lessons-i-wish-id-known-starting-out-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20my%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20feeling%20drained%20from%20getting%20to%20and%20from%20work.%20It's%20also%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20attend%20networking%20events%20in%20the%20area%20after%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238d8ceee-edad-4a0a-ab32-e14ae951503e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%205-day%20RTO%20mandate%20has%20worked%20out%20for%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20from%20the%20office%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20connect%20and%20collaborate%20with%20my%20team.%20When%20everyone%20is%20physically%20around%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20set%20up%20meetings%20for%20every%20small%20discussion.%20You%20can%20just%20walk%20over%2C%20ask%20a%20quick%20question%2C%20and%20keep%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20advantage%20is%20the%20networking%20and%20visibility%2C%20especially%20with%20leaders.%20In%20the%20office%2C%20I%20naturally%20get%20to%20talk%20to%20leaders%20during%20lunch%2C%20coffee%20breaks%2C%20or%20quick%20walks.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20spending%20time%20with%20colleagues%20builds%20a%20healthy%20work%20relationship%3B%20people%20go%20from%20being%20just%20coworkers%20to%20friends%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20work%20environment%20more%20enjoyable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20real%20downside%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-from-home-surviving-return-to-office-mandates-era-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20from%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20five%20days%20a%20week%20is%20on%20days%20when%20I'm%20feeling%20slightly%20unwell%20or%20would%20prefer%20to%20work%20from%20home.%20There's%20been%20a%20stronger%20push%20for%20managers%20and%20teams%20to%20be%20consistently%20in%20the%20office%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-flags-employees-rto-office-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eattendance%20is%20being%20tracked%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20closely.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%20everyone%20is%20present%2C%20there's%20also%20an%20unspoken%20expectation%20of%20being%20on%20time%2C%20which%20reduces%20some%20flexibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20though%2C%20the%20pros%20outweigh%20the%20cons%20by%20a%20large%20margin.%20Even%20when%20Amazon%20had%20a%20hybrid%20setup%20of%20only%20three%20in-office%20days%2C%20I%20preferred%20going%20in%20every%20day%20because%20I%20genuinely%20felt%20more%20productive%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20affected%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-amazon-layoffs-mean-for-your-workplace-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon's%20recent%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%2C%20nor%20was%20anyone%20on%20my%20team%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I'm%20aware.%20In%20terms%20of%20job%20security%2C%20I%20think%20many%20employees%20have%20adopted%20a%20more%20pragmatic%20mindset%2C%20focusing%20on%20delivering%20impact%20and%20doing%20their%20best%20work%2C%20while%20accepting%20that%20some%20factors%20are%20outside%20individual%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20my%20role%20as%20a%20data%20scientist%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20transitioned%20to%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20hasn't%20changed%20much%2C%20and%20I'm%20really%20happy%20with%20the%20work%20I'm%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222396e971-bcd8-4954-987c-6ec223403fb1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20advice%20for%20job%20seekers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20hobbies%20is%20mentoring%20other%20job%20seekers%20I%20connect%20with%2C%20offering%20free%20advice%20on%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20interview%20prep%2C%20and%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-search-tool-apply-dream-role-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincorporate%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20their%20job%20searches.%20Some%20have%20told%20me%20my%20guidance%20helped%20them%20land%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20pieces%20of%20advice%20I%20give%20job%20seekers%20is%20to%20start%20preparing%20for%20interviews%20before%20they%20even%20land%20one%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20keep%20preparing%20throughout%20the%20entire%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20emphasize%20the%20importance%20of%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20%E2%80%94%20a%20candidate%20should%20be%20able%20to%20clearly%20explain%20and%20stand%20behind%20every%20word%20on%20it.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%2099%25%20of%20questions%20trace%20back%20to%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20how%20it%20aligns%20with%20the%20job%20description.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20young%20professional%20lands%20a%20job%2C%20I%20recommend%20that%20they%20live%20close%20to%20the%20office%20if%20they%20can.%20It%20frees%20up%20time%20they'd%20otherwise%20spend%20commuting%20and%20lets%20them%20focus%20that%20energy%20on%20work%2C%20networking%2C%20and%20building%20connections%20with%20colleagues%2C%20all%20of%20which%20really%20help%20them%20settle%20into%20the%20new%20role%20smoothly.%20That%20initial%20period%20is%20crucial%20for%20building%20their%20presence%20and%20making%20a%20strong%20impression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-data-scientist-seattle-short-commute-return-to-office-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773392701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2b946a96e437d6eb83018%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-data-scientist-seattle-short-commute-return-to-office-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarthak%20Gupta%20moved%20to%20Seattle%20before%20landing%20a%20job%20at%20Amazon.%20He%20now%20lives%20walking%20distance%20from%20the%20office%20and%20says%20it's%20helped%20his%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-data-scientist-seattle-short-commute-return-to-office-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20burning%20questions%20hanging%20over%20Nvidia's%20GTC%20summit%20next%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224904%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20speaking%20at%20an%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b060c882b35e2c04dd7216%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENvidia%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang.%3Cp%3ECaroline%20Brehman%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENext%20week%2C%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20will%20take%20the%20stage%20at%20its%20annual%20GTC%20conference.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20expect%20updates%20to%20the%20new%20inference%20chip%20and%20GPU%20roadmaps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGeopolitics%20could%20shape%20Nvidia's%20future%20as%20much%20as%20demand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGTC%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20its%20biggest%20stage%20for%20outlining%20the%20future%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20event%20increasingly%20attracts%20a%20broader%20crowd.%20At%20past%20gatherings%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-2025-ceo-jensen-huang-ai-landscape-san-jose-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDenny's%20pop-ups%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Taiwan-inspired%20night%20markets%2C%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20has%20unveiled%20sweeping%20product%20roadmaps%20for%20its%20GPUs%20and%20other%20AI%20chips.%20It's%20also%20announced%20major%20pacts%20with%20tech%20giants%20and%20governments%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20event%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20a%20blockbuster%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-takeaways-from-nvidias-q4-earnings-vera-rubin-chips-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearnings%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20barely%20nudged%20the%20company's%20stock%20and%20raises%20questions%20about%20how%20long%20the%20AI%20spending%20boom%20can%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolymarket%20users%20are%20even%20wagering%20how%20many%20times%20Huang%20will%20utter%20phrases%20like%20%26quot%3BGPU%26quot%3B%20onstage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20analysts%20and%20investors%20will%20be%20watching%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e461db50-9507-493b-aaa3-a2be7c54aeea%5C%22%3E1.%20A%20new%20inference%20chip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInference%2C%20or%20running%20trained%20models%2C%20is%20AI's%20next%20act.%20Expect%20Nvidia%20to%20make%20a%20big%20statement%20as%20competitors%20%E2%80%94%20from%20cloud%20giants%20to%20a%20slew%20of%20chip%20startups%20%E2%80%94%20encroach%20on%20this%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20previously%20teased%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20new%20chips%20the%20world%20has%20never%20seen%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20in%20February%20that%20Nvidia%20is%20readying%20an%20inference-focused%20product%20incorporating%20technology%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-reaches-licensing-agreement-with-groq-hires-ai-top-talent-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20startup%20Groq%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20OpenAI%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20key%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chip's%20design%20could%20have%20big%20supply%20chain%20implications.%20Inference%20relies%20heavily%20on%20memory%2C%20and%20with%20high%20bandwidth%20memory%20(HBM)%20in%20tight%20supply%2C%20investors%20will%20see%20whether%20Nvidia%20leans%20more%20on%20SRAM%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fast%2C%20on-chip%20memory%20used%20in%20inference%20designs%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20solely%20relying%20on%20HBM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESid%20Sheth%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20inference%20chip%20startup%20d-Matrix%2C%20said%20that%20while%20Nvidia%20will%20stay%20dominant%20in%20training%2C%20%26quot%3Binference%20is%20a%20different%20ballgame.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-cuda-software-gpu-ai-chips-cerebras-ipo-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECUDA%2C%20Nvidia's%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20underpins%20most%20AI%20training%20and%20has%20locked%20developers%20into%20its%20ecosystem%2C%20is%20less%20of%20a%20moat%20in%20inference.%20Developers%20can%20turn%20to%20competitors%20other%20than%20Nvidia%20because%20running%20finished%20AI%20models%20doesn't%20require%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20programming%20as%20training%20them%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7dd26e6-adbc-448b-9030-8ba5cfc2ad89%5C%22%3E2.%20Life%20after%20Rubin%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20has%20announced%20its%20next-generation%20Rubin%20Ultra%20systems.%20Rubin%20is%20expected%20to%20require%20far%20more%20power%20than%20past%20generations%2C%20and%20investors%20will%20eagerly%20see%20how%20Nvidia%20manages%20the%20transition%20and%20whether%20cloud%20giants%20will%20support%20it%2C%20said%20Sebastien%20Naji%2C%20a%20research%20analyst%20at%20William%20Blair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaji%20is%20also%20listening%20for%20what%20comes%20next%3A%20the%20Feynman%20generation.%20The%20big%20architectural%20breakthrough%20expected%20here%20is%20%26quot%3Bcopackaged%20optics%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20use%20of%20light%20%E2%80%94%20not%20electricity%20%E2%80%94%20to%20move%20data%20between%20chips.%20This%20reduces%20power%20consumption%20and%20enables%20larger%20AI%20infrastructure%20clusters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Nvidia%20announced%20it%20secured%20multibillion-dollar%20supply%20agreements%20with%20optical%20component%20companies%20Coherent%20and%20Lumentum%2C%20signaling%20how%20central%20the%20technology%20could%20become%20in%20future%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281386b42-ec36-4093-9f5d-1d0b224348e6%5C%22%3E3.%20Can%20agents%20and%20robots%20keep%20the%20AI%20Gold%20Rush%20alive%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Nvidia%20matures%2C%20investors%20increasingly%20focus%20on%20durability%20rather%20than%20breakneck%20growth%2C%20said%20Brian%20Mulberry%2C%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20Zacks%20Investment%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20has%20emphasized%20agentic%20AI%20as%20the%20next%20driver%20of%20inference%20demand%2C%20a%20trend%20that%20recently%20reverberated%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-cowork-legal-plugin-publishing-stocks-legalzoom-thomson-reuters-relx-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sheth%2C%20the%20d-Matrix%20CEO%2C%20says%20that's%20only%20the%20beginning%2C%20with%20voice%2C%20video%2C%20and%20multimodal%20agents%20that%20have%20yet%20to%20show%20their%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20even%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20a%20forthcoming%20inference%20wave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobotics%20could%20add%20yet%20another%20layer%2C%20said%20Daniel%20Newman%2C%20CEO%20of%20The%20Futurum%20Group.%20Sometimes%20seen%20as%20a%20longer-term%20bet%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20Nvidia%20reported%20roughly%20%246%20billion%20in%20robotics-related%20revenue%20last%20quarter%20and%20is%20predicting%20an%20%26quot%3Baggressive%26quot%3B%20timetable%20for%20humanoids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3ee6188-ee84-4120-8b0d-683bd5b9557d%5C%22%3E4.%20The%20geopolitics%20of%20GPUs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-october-jensen-huang-praises-trump-nokia-deal-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuang%20has%20entered%20the%20political%3C%2Fa%3E%20fray%20at%20past%20GTCs%2C%20and%20the%20landscape%20is%20shifting%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20halted%20production%20of%20H200%20chips%20for%20China%20and%20shifted%20capacity%20to%20its%20next-generation%20Rubin%20platform%2C%20The%20Financial%20Times%20reported.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20US%20is%20weighing%20export%20restrictions%20on%20AI%20chips%20that%20could%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20gatekeeper%20for%20international%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20China%20constrained%2C%20Newman%20said%20international%20markets%20are%20meaningful%20to%20Nvidia%2C%20pointing%20to%20massive%20AI%20infrastructure%20commitments%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20UAE%20%E2%80%94%20though%20conflicts%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20sovereign%20demand%2C%20supply%20chains%2C%20energy%20costs%2C%20and%20the%20pace%20of%20data%20center%20buildouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20AI%20is%20becoming%20a%20geopolitical%20tool%2C%20policy%20could%20shape%20Nvidia's%20future%20as%20much%20as%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agweiss%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Egweiss%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%40geoffweiss.25.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Esharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-gpu-plans-global-tensions-4-big-questions-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773392401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b060c882b35e2c04dd7216%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-gpu-plans-global-tensions-4-big-questions-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nvidia's%20GTC%20faces%20big%20questions%20on%20inference%2C%20next-generation%20GPUs%2C%20and%20how%20geopolitics%20could%20shape%20its%20next%20phase%20of%20growth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gweiss%40businessinsider.com%20(Geoff%20Weiss)%22%2C%22eng