22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224140%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b3c75fa96e437d6eb841bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20that%20he%20is%20looking%20at%20xAI's%20interview%20history%20to%20scan%20for%20missed%20talent.%3Cp%3EFabrice%20COFFRINI%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20he%20is%20revisiting%20old%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20submitted%20to%20xAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20string%20of%20cofounders%20have%20left%20the%20startup%20since%20January.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20week%2C%20Musk%20acknowledged%20the%20startup's%20setup%20issues%20and%20said%20the%20same%20happened%20with%20Tesla.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20combing%20old%20interviews%20as%20high-profile%20employees%20continue%20to%20exit%20his%20AI%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20talented%20people%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20were%20declined%20an%20offer%20or%20even%20an%20interview%20%40xAI.%20My%20apologies%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20in%20a%20Friday%20morning%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20added%20that%20he%20and%20Baris%20Akis%2C%20who%20works%20on%20the%20xAI%20talent%20engineering%20team%2C%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20through%20the%20company%20interview%20history%20and%20reaching%20back%20out%20to%20promising%20candidates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hiring%20efforts%20come%20as%20xAI's%20exodus%20of%20cofounders%20continues.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-cofounders-guodong-zhang-zihang-dai-depart-elon-musk-company-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZihang%20Dai%20left%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20and%20Guodong%20Zhang%20has%20told%20people%20he%20plans%20to%20leave%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20departures%20follow%20the%20recent%20exits%20of%20a%20string%20of%20xAI%20cofounders%2C%20including%20Toby%20Pohlen%2C%20Jimmy%20Ba%2C%20Tony%20Wu%2C%20and%20Greg%20Yang%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20have%20left%20since%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20launched%20xAI%2C%20the%20maker%20of%20Grok%2C%20in%202023%20alongside%2011%20other%20cofounders%20to%20compete%20with%20rival%20frontier%20labs%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Google.%20After%20Dai%20and%20Zhang's%20departures%2C%20only%20two%20of%20the%2011%20people%20who%20started%20the%20company%20with%20Musk%20in%202023%20%E2%80%94%20Manuel%20Kroiss%20and%20Ross%20Nordeen%20%E2%80%94%20will%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20announced%20last%20month%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-all-hands-new-structure-recording-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereorganized%20xAI%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20parted%20ways%20with%20some%20staffers.%20Some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-leadership-style-big-year-grok-ipo-spacex-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecuts%20have%20impacted%20workers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20company's%20AI%20white%20collar%20project%2C%20Macrohard%2C%20and%20Grok%20Imagine%2C%20its%20AI%20image%20and%20video%20generator%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20cofounders'%20departures%2C%20Musk%20has%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20startup's%20shortfalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BxAI%20was%20not%20built%20right%20first%20time%20around%2C%20so%20is%20being%20rebuilt%20from%20the%20foundations%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20on%20X%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BSame%20thing%20happened%20with%20Tesla.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Musk%20said%20at%20the%20Abundance%20Summit%20that%20%26quot%3BGrok%20is%20currently%20behind%20in%20coding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20I%20was%20late%20for%20this%20was%20that%20I%20was%20just%20in%20a%20giant%20sort%20of%20all-hands%20on%20coding%2C%20going%20through%20all%20the%20things%20that%20need%20to%20happen%20to%20essentially%20exceed%20our%20competitors%20on%20coding%2C%20which%20I%20think%20we'll%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20February%2C%20Musk%20announced%20that%20his%20space%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-acquiring-xai-deal-elon-musk-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESpaceX%20would%20acquire%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20xAI.%20XAI%20purchased%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20in%20March%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-missed-good-talent-startup-interview-cofounder-exodus-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773390650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b3c82ea7a4f9df67ba47fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-missed-good-talent-startup-interview-cofounder-exodus-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20said%20he's%20resifting%20through%20past%20xAI%20candidates%20as%20high-profile%20employees%20continue%20to%20exit%20his%20AI%20startup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-missed-good-talent-startup-interview-cofounder-exodus-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20%244.6%20bn%20mistake%3A%20How%20India%20chased%20silver%20to%20%24120%20but%20blinked%20at%20the%20dip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773390615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-02%2F05%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1770262417-3143.jpg%22%2C%