-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T213822.115_11zon-1756742924-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T213822.115_11zon-1756742924-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T213822.115_11zon-1756742924-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-494885%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20fresh%20air%2C%20natural%20beauty%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20adventure%2C%20Karnala%20makes%20the%20perfect%20destination%20for%20a%20relaxed%20family%20getaway%3B%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40hegdevikhyat%2Fkarnala-fort-trek-914198736bbe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPicture%20source%3A%20Medium%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20in%20Panvel%2C%20check%20into%20a%20budget-friendly%20lodge%20or%20hotel.%20Good%20options%20near%20the%20station%20offer%20family%20rooms%20for%20around%20Rs%20800%20to%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20night%2C%20with%20basic%20amenities%20like%20clean%20beds%2C%20attached%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20Wi-Fi.%20Some%20hotels%20may%20offer%20early%20check-in%20if%20requested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUse%20the%20day%20to%20relax%20after%20travel.%20Visit%20Panvel%20Market%2C%20known%20for%20its%20bustling%20vegetable%20stalls%2C%20fruit%20vendors%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F423575%2Fmumbai-snack-seller-mansukh-dada-farsan-seller-borivali-west-jain-derasar-determination%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20snack%20shops%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dinner%20can%20be%20kept%20affordable%20with%20simple%20Maharashtrian%20thalis%20or%20dishes%20lik