0is%20ideal%20for%20the%20moderate%20trek%20to%20Karnala%20Fort.%20Start%20early%20to%20avoid%20the%20afternoon%20heat.%20The%20fort%20trail%20begins%20inside%20the%20sanctuary%20and%20covers%20about%20three%20to%20four%20kilometres%20one%20way%2C%20with%20an%20ascent%20of%20one%20and%20a%20half%20to%20two%20hours%20through%20lush%20forest%20and%20rocky%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trek%20is%20suitable%20for%20families%20with%20children%20aged%20eight%20and%20above.%20Along%20the%20route%2C%20you%20will%20pass%20tall%20bamboo%20groves%2C%20mossy%20rocks%2C%20and%20open%20views%20of%20the%20surrounding%20hills.%20At%20the%20summit%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236682%2Fmumbai-one-day-offbeat-weekend-getaways-travel-holiday-waterfall-nature-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKarnala%20Fort%2C%20built%20in%20the%2012th%20century%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20offers%20breathtaking%20360-degree%20views%20of%20the%20Sahyadri%20ranges%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpend%20time%20at%20the%20top%20soaking%20in%20the%20scenery%20before%20heading%20back%20down.%20Carry%20sufficient%20water%2C%20insect%20repellent%2C%20and%20wear%20comfortable%20shoes.%20Avoid%20feeding%20the%20monkeys%20that%20often%20appear%20near%20resting%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReturn%20to%20your%20lodge%20for%20a%20late%20lunch%20and%20rest.%20Use%20the%20evening%20for%20leisure%2C%20like%20reading%2C%20playing%20games%2C%20or%20taking%20a%20gentle%20stroll%20around%20Panvel%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214731.827_11zon-1756743485.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Karnala%20Bird%20Sanctuary%20enforces%20a%20strict%20no-plastic%20