.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-300x219.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-500x365.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-768x560.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-150x109.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20relief%20requirements%20of%20the%20people%20who%20are%20being%20sheltered%20at%20camps%20after%20being%20rescued%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESchools%20%26amp%3B%20gurudwaras%20turn%20into%20relief%20camps%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20necessity%20of%20boats%20during%20this%20time%2C%20Harmeet%20shares%20that%20these%20are%20of%20paramount%20importance%20in%20the%20Fazilka%20area%20of%20Punjab.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20where%20the%20rivers%20meet%2C%20and%20so%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20flood%20is%20a%20lot.%20The%20water%20has%20increased%20to%20a%20high%20level%20here.%E2%80%9D%20Boats%20are%20the%20only%20form%20of%20conveyance%20right%20now%20across%20the%20districts%20of%20Punjab%3A%20Gurdaspur%2C%20Pathankot%2C%20Ferozepur%2C%20Amritsar%2C%20and%20Fazilka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20Punjab%2C%20gurudwaras%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20other%20public%20institutions%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20relief%20camps.%20The%20Kalgidhar%20Trust%20runs%20100%2B%20schools%2C%20and%20these%20too%20have%20been%20transformed%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F432303%2Fnon-profit-organisations-helping-conflict-affected-communities-india-manipur-kashmir-pahalgam-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecentres%20w